# 🦷 Product Requirements Document (PRD)

## Product Name: Dentify – Smart Dental CRM Platform

---

## 1. 📌 Product Overview

Dentify is a full-stack web application built using Next.js that enables dental clinics to manage their digital presence and patient interactions through an integrated CRM (Customer Relationship Management) system.

The platform serves two primary user groups:
- Patients (Public Website Users)
- Clinic/Admin (CRM Dashboard Users)

---

## 2. 🎯 Objectives

- Build a scalable full-stack application using Next.js
- Centralize patient and appointment data in a CRM
- Enable seamless appointment booking
- Improve clinic efficiency and patient experience

---

## 3. 👥 User Roles

### 3.1 Patient (Public User)
- Browse services
- View dentist profile
- Book appointments
- Contact clinic

### 3.2 Admin (Clinic User)
- Manage appointments
- Manage patient data
- Manage services and content
- View analytics

---

## 4. 🧩 Core Modules

---

### 4.1 🌐 Public Website (Frontend)

**Features:**
- Home Page
- About Page
- Services Pages
- Blog/Articles
- Contact Page
- Appointment Booking

**Tech:**
- Next.js (App Router)
- SEO optimized (SSR/SSG)

---

### 4.2 📅 Appointment System

**Features:**
- Service selection
- Date & time slot booking
- Patient information form
- Data storage in database
- Confirmation system

**CRM Integration:**
- Auto-create/update patient record
- Assign appointment status

---

### 4.3 🧑‍⚕️ CRM Dashboard (Admin Panel)

**Features:**
- Secure login (Admin only)
- Dashboard overview

#### Sections:

**1. Appointments Management**
- View all bookings
- Update status (Pending, Confirmed, Completed, Cancelled)

**2. Patient Management**
- Patient profiles
- Visit history
- Notes

**3. Services Management**
- Add/Edit/Delete services
- Optional pricing

**4. Content Management**
- Blog posts
- Testimonials
- Gallery

**5. Analytics**
- Total bookings
- Monthly performance
- Popular services

---

### 4.4 💬 Communication System

- WhatsApp integration
- Email notifications (optional)
- Appointment reminders (future scope)

---

## 5. 🗄️ Database Design (High-Level)

### Users (Admin)
- id
- name
- email
- password

### Patients
- id
- name
- phone
- email
- history

### Appointments
- id
- patient_id
- service_id
- date
- time
- status

### Services
- id
- name
- description
- price

### Testimonials
- id
- patient_name
- review
- rating

### Blog Posts
- id
- title
- content
- created_at

---

## 6. 🏗️ Tech Stack

### Frontend:
- Next.js (App Router)
- Tailwind CSS
- React Hook Form

### Backend:
- Next.js API Routes / Server Actions

### Database:
- MongoDB or PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM (recommended)

### Authentication:
- NextAuth.js / Auth.js

### Deployment:
- Vercel

---

## 7. 🔐 Security Requirements

- Secure authentication (JWT/session)
- Input validation
- Role-based access control
- Data encryption (sensitive fields)

---

## 8. 📱 UI/UX Requirements

- Mobile-first design
- Clean and minimal interface
- Fast loading (<2 seconds)
- Easy navigation
- Strong CTA buttons (Book Now)

---

## 9. 🔄 User Flow

### Patient Flow:
1. Visit website
2. Browse services
3. Click "Book Appointment"
4. Fill form
5. Submit
6. Appointment stored in CRM

---

### Admin Flow:
1. Login to dashboard
2. View appointments
3. Manage patients/services
4. Update appointment status

---

## 10. 🚀 MVP Scope (Phase 1)

- Public website
- Appointment booking system
- Basic CRM dashboard
- Patient & appointment management

---

## 11. 🔮 Future Enhancements

- AI chatbot
- Online payments
- Patient login dashboard
- SMS/email reminders
- Multi-language support
- Advanced analytics

---

## 12. 📊 Success Metrics

- Weekly bookings
- Conversion rate (visitor → booking)
- User engagement
- CRM usage by admin

---

## 13. 🧠 Product Vision

Dentify is not just a dental website, but a full-stack digital infrastructure that connects patient experience with clinic operations through a centralized CRM system.

---